name: NameShuffle
0:
”Alexa ask name shuffle add panda”
”Alexa ask name shuffle set length to 30”
”Alexa ask name shuffle next”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: name shuffle
des: This skill will help you find a team name. Just add some of the possible names you have come up with. It will randomly choose 3 of these names and output the new fabulous team name. You can change the amount of words in the team name and you can always reshuffle the names to get a new one.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
